msg: This class will act as the invoker for the web services.
Its job is to get a request message from the queue (Already in the
proper order) and invoke the required service using the specified provider.
If there is a response due the invokation then RMInvoker will add it in to the
storage so that it will be sent to the original sender using a different sequence.
